Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.45,0:00:05.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.49,0:00:07.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想拜托柳也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还多少有些难为情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.03,0:00:19.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.39,0:01:54.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.71,0:01:57.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.57,0:02:02.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手包啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过要抛手包吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还漂亮地抛起了三个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.67,0:02:19.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很漂亮地抛起了三个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快回去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在放哨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人要给你看拿手绝活呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做臣子的不是该跪下恭恭敬敬地拜见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.60,0:02:35.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡搅蛮缠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.02,0:02:39.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等！ 等等！ 等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.49,0:02:44.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这种时候用主人的命令来压我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.40,0:02:47.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再立什么多余的誓言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别咬人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不怪你自己太粗暴了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着就是了  你快点抛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的话… 总是这么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:09.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.25,0:03:09.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看想得不得了  你快点抛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么一点诚意也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.03,0:03:17.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过我的绝技之后  你的态度也就会变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于找到窍门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  学会了之后就是这么简单的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我已经是不输给里叶的手包名人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.65,0:03:40.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白  全心全意去学习一件事物是多么地重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.31,0:03:41.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.81,0:03:57.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那绝对是搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的已经学会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没说你说谎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看着呢  你尽管抛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀放松一些嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放松一些的话  名人也做不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.09,0:04:38.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抛得不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到这样已经很了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着安慰我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做成这样  是因为你努力练习了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂得放弃可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂你到底是在夸我还是在嘲笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在夸你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  你干得很好  神奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想做得更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.78,0:05:13.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都练习的话肯定会变得很拿手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.99,0:05:14.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夸张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还会再看我抛手包吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只要你愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在快去睡一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.59,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还要走很多路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.45,0:05:47.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来必须越过这些群山峻岭才行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:53.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃脱追兵的话  在山林里行进是再好不过的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去取些水来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  神奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.20,0:06:12.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你饶了我吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:23.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进不去了… 都说过进不去了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吃不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这么睡的话会感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别再睡第二觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.75,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也别睡第三觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也大人  您太手软了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼的啊  你干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神奈大人  您感觉好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我像感觉好的样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我起床时就不能再温柔些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.76,0:07:28.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次我就再注意一下力度…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是让你别再抽枕头了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.28,0:07:42.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的耳朵可真奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.14,0:07:46.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来的话不会刮到草木上去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.40,0:07:50.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵这么长的话  可以听得很远吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  居然敢耍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  给我停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我停下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 停下停下停下停下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我安静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在看什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.07,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天在集市上找到的地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很珍贵的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些像虫子一样的东西是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河流的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神奈  你不认识字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么可能认识呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里叶居然也不管你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有不管呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.48,0:08:37.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为神奈大人说过「绝对不想跟里叶学字」…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.04,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是要怪里叶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会忘了歌集那件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.89,0:08:46.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了丰富神奈大人的心灵才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你那种教人的方法  心灵怎么会丰富得起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.40,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.64,0:08:55.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前  我曾经教过神奈大人背诵和歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习东西当然要付出一点点心血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.44,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是神奈大人却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.88,0:09:06.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天要背二百首  还叫什么「一点点心血」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有四千五百首呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭怎么行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经五天没睡了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.55,0:09:19.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下二百首  再忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的命还真大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这样下去肯定会死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把歌集全都扔到炉灶里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.28,0:09:34.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贵的古今六帖一并全都变成早饭的柴火了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的饭  真是充满了风流的味道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.15,0:09:44.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这张嘴在胡说八道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开… 里叶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一首和歌也唱不出来的嘴巴  根本就是没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没道理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干脆把它缝上算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:10:01.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我也怕里叶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我有些太激动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.81,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要原谅她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音还是很怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.15,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到那边去练习抛手包了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里待着心会乱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也陪你一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在乱发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.35,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神奈  怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.98,0:11:02.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和尚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上没有伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是累倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说一会话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.49,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要抛手包吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有什么心事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.14,0:11:36.78,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.11,0:11:41.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想说的话不必憋在心里  把它说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就说一句好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:48.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头顶上有只毛毛虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.72,0:11:59.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很容易吸引野兽和虫子之类的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么冷静啊  就不能救救我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就一直觉得你很古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想作为主人关心一下臣子来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果弄得自己这么没面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我说给你听就是了  别走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再拿我开玩笑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.29,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是很无聊的事情哦  你真的想听吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没见过自己的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  是被扔掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路边哭泣的时候  被行脚僧捡到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行脚僧就是旅行的和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的行脚僧听起来似乎很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.87,0:12:46.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也只是无家可归  四处乞讨的人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.37,0:12:51.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩一起周游了各种各样的土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:55.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方 南方 东方 西方  去过各种各样的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是柳也的养育之亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上是什么养育之亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.49,0:13:07.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个严厉的人  除了诵经之外从不开口说闲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.23,0:13:10.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连法名最终也没有告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大约五岁时的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在山路上遇到了山贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行脚僧被一刀杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.94,0:13:28.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到刚才那个和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.26,0:13:35.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来柳也也没有母亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.74,0:13:41.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我却只顾追寻自己的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.02,0:13:42.98,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个行脚僧临死前还在祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.78,0:13:54.87,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝愿杀死自己的人能够往升净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后  自己死在了血泊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说我不值得弄脏他们的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  我又独自一人站在路边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后  我一直都是一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！ 追！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去  我什么都干过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.08,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷走过别人的刀枪  参加过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.74,0:14:25.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也杀过人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都只想着自己如何才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最近为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近发生过什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的心境转变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一些契机  人都会改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.18,0:14:48.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些山贼一定也很后悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们杀了一位德高望重的高僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会后悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.67,0:14:57.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难说他能不能算得上是德高望重的高僧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怀疑什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为听到了行脚僧的祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.73,0:15:06.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山贼们才没有杀害柳也吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.98,0:15:13.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.05,0:15:18.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  我或许确实是被行脚僧救了一条命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.79,0:15:22.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有早点注意到这一点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.23,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  我就一定会走上另一条道路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.25,0:15:30.32,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  我不是就遇不到柳也了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也庆幸自己能遇到神奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.12,0:15:47.80,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道接下来该怎么做才好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.17,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.43,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后边的事就拜托给柳也了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.39,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很难为情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.69,0:16:11.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的知道接下来要干什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别… 别小看我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.65,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里叶全都教给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.26,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是里叶捣的鬼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:26.79,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也对我来说就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说不清楚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.50,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里叶说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.61,0:16:43.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「柳也说起往事的时候  就别放过那个机会」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.67,0:16:49.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性是一定会对喜欢的女性说起往事来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被她猜中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.23,0:16:58.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「听柳也说完后  就慢慢地解开衣服」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.89,0:17:03.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还说过什么「需要让胸部若隐若现」之类的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连导演都做好了吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.47,0:17:08.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄错什么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非  柳也只喜欢男色吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.57,0:17:16.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.86,0:17:20.02,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些男性虽然喜欢女性  却很无能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是因为把衣服脱得过头了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.45,0:17:27.47,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.11,0:17:32.51,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你知道我也是个男人  你做好准备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也  你的眼神很怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.93,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你来引诱我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就老老实实让我用毒牙咬一口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳… 柳也有毒的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人全都是有毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.95,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有更多你不知道的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我一步一步教你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快住手！ 住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.84,0:17:57.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.82,0:18:01.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里叶  你藏在那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.22,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你依然是那么精明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.85,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神奈大人  您没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.10,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚… 不过似乎不太成功…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.76,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.21,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我惹柳也生气了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是看穿我绝对不会出手的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.04,0:18:38.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我自己也不是很确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.16,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下哪还有我这种人畜无害的男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.53,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是无能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.77,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她睡得很香嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.74,0:18:58.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也热心地做过手包的修炼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.23,0:19:03.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着的时候  倒是很可爱的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无聊男人们聚过来之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得教会她色恋之事才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用我来练习啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还是个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连人偶和手包都没有玩过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一个梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.62,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个在其他地方的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.08,0:19:35.00,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿着奇特的衣装  相貌也改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是我吗…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成什么样的相貌了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.71,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  身边有我的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多善良的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常地幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很好的梦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把这个梦变成现实不就行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.67,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上就能见到母亲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.96,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  你的梦就不再是梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.79,0:20:10.82,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要虔诚祈祷  上天就一定能够听到我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.34,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.62,0:20:25.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做得很好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.84,0:20:27.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们没有掉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个也没有掉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.92,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还需要再修炼一段时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.69,0:20:52.64,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真的是很棒啊  神奈大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.07,0:20:57.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要继续修炼下去  一定会更加出色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.55,0:20:58.48,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:02.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我就可以做给母亲看了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.37,0:21:03.61,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.45,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该走了  神奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  不和我一起来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的母亲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.19,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.44,0:21:47.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要永远幸福地生活下去啊


